    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Empire of Froge has fallen, but in your last stand, your comrades suddenly re-grow in numbers! This is Frogmageddon! A Bullet Heaven-style survival game where the more evil snakes you defeat, the larger your frog army grows (to the hundreds!).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow your army!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/6e221dea9088a9a03df057c5ea4022dc.poster.avif?t=1762704763\" width=634 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/6e221dea9088a9a03df057c5ea4022dc.webm?t=1762704763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/6e221dea9088a9a03df057c5ea4022dc.mp4?t=1762704763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every defeated snake poses an opportunity to amass more frogs. But watch out: each frog  can only take one hit before being lost to the fires of war. Master your positioning to maximize the growth of your pond-dwelling platoon!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weaponized Frogs!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/473a5b3b6dc0e93ca145854ed7ddd13c.poster.avif?t=1762704763\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/473a5b3b6dc0e93ca145854ed7ddd13c.webm?t=1762704763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/473a5b3b6dc0e93ca145854ed7ddd13c.mp4?t=1762704763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More frogs means more damage! New frogs have a chance of spawning a variety of weapons to help in defeating the snake menace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the Liliad!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What led to the fall of the Frogean Empire? How can Frogean kind repopulate? Find out in the epic <span class=\"bb_strike\">time-waster</span> tale detailing the fall and hopeful return of the Frogean Empire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Exclusive Features!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your friends will know you play Frogmageddon.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And many more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the frog! Live the frog!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/2c549deeb2fd21ee8fab9165f2d978f4.poster.avif?t=1762704763\" width=540 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201190/extras/2c549deeb2fd21ee8fab9165f2d978f4.webm?t=1762704763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
